# Doculy Verifier (Open Source)

An open-source prototype for **certificate forgery risk detection** using a Vision Transformer (ViT) in a simple Streamlit app.

> ⚠️ Disclaimer: This is a **research / demo tool**, not a production security system. Do not rely on it for real-world decisions.

## Features (v0.1)

- Upload a certificate image (`.png`, `.jpg`, `.jpeg`)
- Run it through a pre-trained ViT model
- Show a simple "forgery risk" score (heuristic for now)

## Getting Started

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/doculy-verifier.git
cd doculy-verifier
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
